to the editor re broken promises and political deception by al gore op ed aug 4 as if the events of sept 11 were not enough the american people have had to contemplate in the last few months another tragedy the collapse of the american dream of prosperity liberty and justice for all just as we must now rebuild lower manhattan we must now with equal devotion do all that we can to resurrect this dream mr gore 's eloquent essay unlike so many of his earlier pronouncements has the ring of sincerity he might well be the national reformer whom we now so desperately need at this time of mounting cynicism and despair philip walker santa barbara calif aug 4 2002

